{
  "DARV.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.ancient": "哇！我们这是有多久没见了呀？！……等等，还是说，你是过去的那个你！？",
  "DARV.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-1.char": "[i][font_size=22]时空魔女摇了摇头，又点了点头。[/font_size][/i]",
  "DARV.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.1-0r.ancient": "又见面了！来来，看看这堆东西，随便挑一个去吧！",
  "DARV.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.ancient": "嘿，你之前给我的那个东西，在我这儿放了这么久，还挺好用的！不过我想，也差不多是时候让它物归原主啦！",
  "DARV.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.next": "婉拒",
  "DARV.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.char": "[i][font_size=22]时空魔女摇了摇头，从裂隙中拿出了一个一模一样的。[/font_size][/i]",
  "DARV.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-2.ancient": "哎呀！你竟然还有一个一模一样的？！哈哈，那我就不客气地把它继续收在我的宝堆里啦！",

  "NEOW.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.char": "[sine]...这么久... 你又... ..来到了.. 这里...[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-1.ancient": "[sine]...只要.. 能.. ..杀死.. [red][jitter]建筑师[/jitter][/red]...[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.1-0r.ancient": "[sine]...你.. 又... ..回来了...[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.ancient": "[sine]...为何.. ..不.. 杀死.. [red]建筑师[/red]...？[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.next": "无视",
  "NEOW.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.char": "[i][font_size=22]时空魔女没有在意。[/font_size][/i]",
  "NEOW.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-2.ancient": "[sine]...只要.. 有所... ..帮助...[/sine]",

  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.ancient": "我活了这么久，还从没见到过……像你这样[sine]光彩动人[/sine]的存在。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-1.char": "[i][font_size=22]时空魔女也打量着诺奴佩普。[/font_size][/i]",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.1-0r.ancient": "亲爱的，我觉得这件会很适合你。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.char": "[i][font_size=22]时空魔女将一颗宝珠送给诺奴佩普。[/font_size][/i]",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.ancient": "我收到过无数的奇珍异宝，但你的这件礼物……真是让我看到了无与伦比的美丽。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-2.ancient": "[i][font_size=22]诺奴佩普一直盯着宝珠[/font_size][/i]",

  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.ancient": "从来没见过！！这样的存在！！你是什么？？",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.next": "展示",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-1.char": "[i][font_size=22]时空魔女让一只手缓缓消散一半又凝聚到一起[/font_size][/i]",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-1.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-2.ancient": "[jitter]哇啊啊！！[/jitter] 好厉害！！好特别！！你是怎么做到的？？再多展示一点！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-2.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-3.char": "[i][font_size=22]时空魔女轻声讲述着原理。[/font_size][/i]",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.1-0r.ancient": "再说说！！更多！！更多有趣的事情！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.ancient": "那本书！！里面装了什么？？故事？秘密？？快告诉我！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.next": "展示",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.char": "[i][font_size=22]时空魔女将书本打开，每一页都浮现出一个其他时空的画面。[/font_size][/i]",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-2.ancient": "[jitter]哇啊啊啊！！[/jitter] 每一页都在动！！好多世界！！好多画面！！这是怎么装进去的？？太神奇了！！想看！！想看！！！",

  "PAEL.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.ancient": "[thinky_dots]我好像梦见过你……很久以前……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-1.ancient": "[thinky_dots]很久……很久……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.1-0r.ancient": "[thinky_dots]过来……拿走我的一部分吧……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.ancient": "[thinky_dots]我能感觉到……你沉眠的时间……比我还要久……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.next": "沉默",
  "PAEL.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.char": "[i][font_size=22]时空魔女没有回答。[/font_size][/i]",
  "PAEL.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.next": "等待",
  "PAEL.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-2.ancient": "[i][font_size=22]佩尔在漫长的沉默中睡了过去。[/font_size][/i]",

  "TANX.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.ancient": "[b]强大的存在！！来与我一战！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.next": "进入相位空间",
