  "TANX.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-1.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-2.ancient": "[b]出来！！堂堂正正地与我战斗！！[/b]",
