  "TEZCATARA.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.char": "[i][font_size=22]时空魔女提着一篮饼干造访特兹卡特拉[/font_size][/i]",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-0.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.ancient": "哎呀呀，亲爱的！你回来看望我这个老太婆，还带了[jitter][b]饼干[/b][/jitter]！真是贴心的小可爱，快过来，让我好好看看你！",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-1.next": "休息",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.2-2.char": "[i][font_size=22]二人一同享用了点心。[/font_size][/i]",

  "VAKUU.talk.SPACE_TIME_WITCH_CHARACTER_SPACE_TIME_WITCH.0-0.ancient": "[jitter]你拒绝契约...就是预见了我会有今天这副模样么？![/jitter]",
